                <span class="text-3xl mr-4">💧</span>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900">Izvori materijala</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Osnovno je pravilo da se bakterije mogu izolirati iz tekuće faze – suspenzije.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-3">Tipovi suspenzija:</h4>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-center">🩸 Krv</span>
                  <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-center">👄 Slina</span>
